On or about November 7, 2021 WSDOT GIS Data Download website will redirect website traffic to the WSDOT Geospatial Open Data site.
attributes.reason_for_change: WSDOT's Internet site is being redesigned. The new site will be far more streamlined, mobile friendly, and accessible. The move to an Open Data platform allows WSDOT to continue to share our geospatial data to the public.
attributes.additional_information: Both the "old" and "new" WSDOT GIS Data download sites are provided in the Informational URL sections. Please note that the "go live" date for the new website is tentative. Be assured, the current download site won't disappear BEFORE November 7th, but it will change sometime after November 7th. This website update affects all WSDOT webpages, not just the GIS Data Download page.
